## Pattern Matching: Exhaustive match (Ch 15)

**Before:**
```rust
let opt: Option<i32> = get_value();
match opt {
    Some(x) => println!("{x}"),
    _ => {}  // silently ignores None — intent unclear
}
```
**After:**
```rust
